## 💻 Développement

### Structure technique
```
apps/math4child/
├── src/app/api/stripe/           # API Routes Stripe
├── src/hooks/useStripe.ts        # Hooks React
├── src/types/stripe.ts           # Types TypeScript
├── src/lib/stripe.ts             # Configuration Stripe
└── src/components/stripe/        # Composants UI
```

### Utilisation dans le code
```typescript
import { useStripe } from '@/hooks/useStripe'

function SubscribeButton() {
  const { loading, error, createCheckoutForPlan } = useStripe()
  
  const handleSubscribe = () => {
    createCheckoutForPlan('premium', 'user@example.com')
  }
  
  return (
    <button onClick={handleSubscribe} disabled={loading}>
      S'abonner Premium
    </button>
  )
}
```

